Package: rtika
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to 'Apache Tika' 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sasha Goodman <goodmansasha@gmail.com>[aut], The Apache Software Foundation [aut,cph]
Maintainer: Sasha Goodman <goodmansasha@gmail.com>
Suggests: sys, jsonlite, xml2, data.table
License: Apache License 2.0 | file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: Java (>=7) | openjdk-7-jre (via apt) | java-1.7.0-openjdk (via yum) | openjdk-8-jre (via apt) | java-1.8.0-openjdk (via yum) 
Description: Extract text and metadata from over a thousand file types. Get either plain text or structured XHTML. This R interface includes the Tika program. Its source is available at https://tika.apache.org/. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
